Installing TeX Live at CSE:

Instructions at https://tug.org/texlive/quickinstall.html .
(Longer instructions at https://tug.org/texlive/doc/texlive-en/texlive-en.html .)


# This takes a loong time to install.
cd ~/bin/install
wget https://mirror.ctan.org/systems/texlive/tlnet/install-tl-unx.tar.gz
tar zxf install-tl-unx.tar.gz
cd install-tl-20251030
perl install-tl --texdir=$HOME/bin/install/texlive/2025
# Set default paper size to letter by typing:  o p r
# Start installation by typing:  i

